Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:08.46,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}晴れに晴れ、花よ咲け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:12.68,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}咲いて晴るのせい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:17.06,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}降り止めば雨でさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:21.73,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}貴方を飾る晴る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:27.36,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}胸を打つ音よ凪げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:31.45,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}僕ら晴る風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:35.78,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}あの雲も越えてゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}遠くまだ遠くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:27.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你就像风一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:31.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}闭上眼 已是黄昏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:37.23,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你在想些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:45.90,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}睁开双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:50.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你的眼眸晶莹透亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:57.33,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}散发着丝丝晴的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:08.46,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}晴空万里 花开遍地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:12.68,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}百花皆为晴而开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:17.06,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}就连初晴后的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:21.73,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}也是装饰于你的晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:27.36,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}心中的悸动啊化作细风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:31.45,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我们亦化为晴风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:35.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}穿过那片云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}直到天边
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:33.79,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}And you alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.78,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}Can you hear me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.46,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}誰もいない線路沿いをなぞってく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.93,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}大袈裟に泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:48.75,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}笑ってほしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:55.24,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}鮮明でいたい思い出を抱きしめている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:23:01.63,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}さよならよりずっと大切な　言葉で伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:07.40,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}ありふれて　でも特別で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.92,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:13.89,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}見えなかったものが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:18.71,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}どうして？　溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:24.72,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}だから　もう一度　生まれ変わろうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:30.64,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}また　私はここを選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:36.64,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}だから　あなたと　また巡り逢ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:42.32,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}もう離さない　今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:45.22,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}約束なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.32,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}孤独に迷う日々でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:54.31,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}その涙だって大丈夫　きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:58.54,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,0)\blur3}I’m whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:01.35,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(0,360)\blur3}I’m whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.89,0:22:33.79,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}你还好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.78,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}你听得见我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.46,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}独自漫步在无人的铁道线上
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.93,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}时而嚎啕大哭
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.71,0:22:48.75,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}时而逗你欢笑
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.38,0:22:55.24,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}抱紧记忆里不想淡去的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:23:01.63,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}想用比告别更珍贵的话语告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:07.40,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}平平无奇 却又独一无二
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.92,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那些曾经只有这双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:13.89,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}才能看见的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:18.71,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}为何如今已随处可见？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:24.72,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}所以即使 获得了新的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:30.64,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也还会选择这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:36.64,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}所以如果 还能与你相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:42.32,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那就永不分离 我还会选择当下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:45.22,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}不需要什么约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.32,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}在孤独迷茫的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:54.31,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}不必强忍泪水 黎明总会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:58.54,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,0)\blur3}我正哼着我们的摇篮曲 等你回家呢
Dialogue: 1,0:23:58.54,0:24:01.35,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(0,360)\blur3}我正哼着我们的摇篮曲 等你回家呢
